text: The Mahabharat ground skink (Asymblepharus mahabharatus) is a species of skink found in Nepal. ==References== Category:Asymblepharus Category:Reptiles described in 1998 Category:Taxa named by Valery Konstantinovich Eremchenko Category:Taxa named by Karan Bahadur Shah Category:Taxa named by Alexander M. Panfilov
title: Asymblepharus mahabharatus
